    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> memoriae <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>eli</ex></expan> Barbae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>erani</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> et Aureli<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/>Probiano <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> l<surplus>i</surplus><expan><abbr>eg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>criptae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Gaudentio et Firmini<lb break="no" n="5"/>ano qui <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> VIII <lb n="6"/>Aurelia Heraclia li<lb break="no" n="7"/>berta ex testame<lb break="no" n="8"/>n<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>o <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden in Wiederverwendung für ein Grab. Das Erhaltene ist in 2 Teile gebrochen. Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Fries mit Opferszene, darüber die Büsten zweier Männer und zweier Kinder. Z. 1: Die Buchstaben D und M befinden sich in der Frieszone. Vágó: Z. 8/9: testame/n(to) of(ficium) c(uravit).</p>
            </div>
